---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const imageSrc = `${base}/images/casting-molds-story.png`;
---

<section class="foundry-story" aria-labelledby="foundry-story-heading">
  <div class="section-rule">
    <h2 id="foundry-story-heading">Foundry story</h2>
    <span class="section-tail">/ why this shape</span>
  </div>

  <div class="story-panel tinted-shadow">
    <div class="story-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Molds into casts</span>
      <h3>Make the knowledge base actionable.</h3>
      <p>
        The Foundry keeps workflow-construction knowledge as inspectable notes: patterns,
        research, CLI docs, schemas, and best practices. Molds turn that rich source record
        into statically validated cast artifacts, so agents can load portable generated skills without
        losing the trail back to the documented reasoning.
      </p>
      <div class="story-actions">
        <a href={`${base}/story/`} class="story-primary">
          Read the full story
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}/glossary/`} class="story-secondary">Glossary</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-art">
      <img
        src={imageSrc}
        alt="Infographic showing a knowledge base pressed through Casting Molds into generated skills and actionable pipelines."
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .foundry-story {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .story-panel {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(16rem, 0.82fr) minmax(26rem, 1.55fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-surface-raised);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .story-copy {
    padding: 0.65rem 0.5rem 0.65rem 0.65rem;
  }
  .story-copy h3 {
    margin: 0.65rem 0 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-galaxy-dark);
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .dark .story-copy h3 {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .story-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .story-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .story-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.52rem 0.9rem;
    background: var(--color-galaxy-dark);
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    border-radius: 0.35rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .story-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-galaxy-primary);
    transform: translateX(2px);
  }
  .story-secondary {
    color: var(--color-link);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-link) 35%, transparent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .story-secondary:hover {
    color: var(--color-link-hover);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .story-art {
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .story-art img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-border-subtle) 70%, transparent);
    border-radius: 0.45rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .story-panel {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .story-panel {
      padding: 0.8rem;
    }
    .story-copy {
      padding: 0.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
